To get oil or tar you need to find a "Bitumen seep" patch and place an oil derrick or a tar extractor upon the resource. The drill you placed down will require both drilling fluid and power for it to start up. After some time for the drill to drill down to the resource, it will stop using the drilling fluid and will begin outputting oil or tar-based on the entity placed on it. the default amount of fluid is between 100,000 and 400,000 per patch. this amount can be increased by both the entities level and the level of drilling fluid used. Max possible increase is x64 base value.

如何找到石油和原油?\nA：要获取石油或焦油，首先需要找到一个[color=blue]待开发的油藏[/color]资源点，然后将石油井架或焦油钻探机放在资源点上。您需要给设备提供[color=blue]钻井液，并供给电力[/color]动力才能启动。经过一段时间的钻探后，设备将停止使用钻井液，并根据放置在其上的设备型号开始输出石油或焦油。每个资源点的默认存液量为100,000至400,000。[color=blue]更好的设备等级和更好的钻井液[/color]可以提高这个数值。最大可能为基础量的64倍。
